<%- include('partials/head') %>
<%- include('partials/header') %>

<main class="container">
  <h2 class="section-title">L'Atelier Story</h2>

  <!-- Narrative Section 1 -->
  <section class="brand-story-teaser" style="margin-top: 40px; border-top: none;">
    <div class="brand-story-grid">
      <div class="brand-story-text">
        <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent-color); letter-spacing: 0.15em; display: block; margin-bottom: 15px;">The Philosophy</span>
        <h3>Sculpting Silhouettes, Preserving Time</h3>
        <p>
          Founded in Paris, Maison Éther was established to resist the accelerate-and-discard cycles of fast-fashion. We treat garment construction not as factory logistics, but as physical architecture. 
        </p>
        <p>
          By creating custom-tailored patterns, drafting cuts directly onto fabric grids, and finishing seams with hand-sewn invisible stitches, we design clothes that develop a singular dialogue with the wearer's body over decades.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="brand-story-image">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1539571696357-5a69c17a67c6?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Couture dress fitting portrait" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Narrative Section 2 -->
  <section class="brand-story-teaser" style="margin-top: 0; border-top: none; border-bottom: none;">
    <div class="brand-story-grid" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 1.2fr;">
      <div class="brand-story-image">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509631179647-0177331693ae?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Premium fabric swatches weave detail" loading="lazy">
      </div>
      <div class="brand-story-text" style="max-width: 550px;">
        <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent-color); letter-spacing: 0.15em; display: block; margin-bottom: 15px;">Artisanal Sourcing</span>
        <h3>The Noble Origin of Fibers</h3>
        <p>
          Our sourcing process is deliberate. We partner exclusively with heritage mills in Biella, Italy for worsted wools, family-run looms in Lyon, France for mulberry silk satins, and sustainable pastoral co-ops in Ulaanbaatar for premium combed cashmeres.
        </p>
        <p>
          We trace every bale of fleece from shearer to spinner. These materials are chosen because they possess a physical weight and breathability that synthetic fibers can never match.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Narrative Section 3 -->
  <section class="brand-story-teaser" style="margin-top: 0; border-bottom: none;">
    <div class="brand-story-grid">
      <div class="brand-story-text">
        <span style="font-size: 0.75rem; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--accent-color); letter-spacing: 0.15em; display: block; margin-bottom: 15px;">Workshop Details</span>
        <h3>Hand-Crafted in France</h3>
        <p>
          Maison Éther operates out of a quiet, sunlit top-floor studio on Rue du Faubourg Saint-Honoré. Here, a tight-knit circle of master cutters, pattern-makers, and finishers assemble each collection. 
        </p>
        <p>
          Each jacket, blazer, or trousers is assigned to a single artisan from initial layout to final stitch. The signature hand-sewn labels inside are hand-numbered to represent this dedicated focus.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="brand-story-image">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1512436991641-6745cdb1723f?q=80&w=800&auto=format&fit=crop" alt="Tailored wool coats hanging on rack" loading="lazy">
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>

<%- include('partials/footer') %>
